Name: TeamID
Description: The auto-generated unique ID of the Team

Name: [Key]
Description: Abbreviation of the team (e.g. LAL; PHI; BOS; CHI; etc.)

Name: Active
Description: Whether or not this team is active

Name: City
Description: The city/location of the team (e.g. Los Angeles; Philadelphia; Boston; Chicago; etc.)

Name: Name
Description: The mascot of the team (e.g. Lakers; 76ers; Celtics; Bulls; etc.)

Name: LeagueID
Description: The league of the team (possible values: Eastern; Western)

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the team's current home stadium

Name: Conference
Description: The conference of the team (possible values: Eastern; Western)

Name: Division
Description: The division of the team (e.g. Atlantic; Central; Southeast; etc)

Name: PrimaryColor
Description: The team's primary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: SecondaryColor
Description: The team's secondary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: TertiaryColor
Description: The team's tertiary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: QuaternaryColor
Description: The team's quaternary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: WikipediaLogoUrl
Description: The link to the team's logo hosted on Wikipedia. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: WikipediaWordMarkUrl
Description: The link to the team's wordmark logo hosted on Wikipedia. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: GlobalTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for this team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: NbaDotComTeamID
Description: The team's ID on nba dot com

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the stadium

Name: Active
Description: Whether or not this stadium is the home venue for an active team

Name: Name
Description: The full name of the stadium

Name: Address
Description: The address where the stadium is located

Name: City
Description: The city where the stadium is located

Name: State
Description: The US state where the stadium is located (if Stadium is outside US; this value is NULL)

Name: Zip
Description: The zip code of the stadium

Name: Country
Description: The 2-digit country code where the stadium is located

Name: Capacity
Description: The estimated seating capacity of the stadium

Name: GeoLat
Description: The geographic latitude coordinate of this venue.

Name: GeoLong
Description: The geographic longitude coordinate of this venue.

Name: GameID
Description: The unique ID of this game

Name: Season
Description: The NBA season of the game

Name: SeasonType
Description: The type of season that this record corresponds to (1=Regular Season; 2=Preseason; 3=Playoffs).

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the game's status. Possible values include: Scheduled; InProgress; Final; F/OT; Suspended; Postponed; Canceled

Name: Day
Description: The date of the game

Name: DateTime
Description: The date and time of the game

Name: AwayTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Away Team

Name: HomeTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Home Team

Name: AwayTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the away team

Name: HomeTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the home team

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the stadium

Name: Channel
Description: The television station broadcasting the game

Name: Attendance
Description: Total number of people who attended the game

Name: AwayTeamScore
Description: Number of points the away scored in this game

Name: HomeTeamScore
Description: Number of points the home scored in this game

Name: Updated
Description: The timestamp of when the record was last updated (US Eastern Time).

Name: Quarter
Description: The current quarter in the game. Possible values include: 1; 2; 3; 4; Half; OT; NULL

Name: TimeRemainingMinutes
Description: Number of minutes remaining in the quarter

Name: TimeRemainingSeconds
Description: Number of seconds remaining in the quarter

Name: PointSpread
Description: The oddsmaker Point Spread at game start from the perspective of the HomeTeam (negative numbers indicate the HomeTeam is favored; positive numbers indicate the AwayTeam is favored)

Name: OverUnder
Description: The oddsmaker Over/Under at game start

Name: AwayTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the away team

Name: HomeTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the home team

Name: GlobalGameID
Description: A globally unique ID for this game. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalAwayTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the away team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalHomeTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the home team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: PointSpreadAwayTeamMoneyLine
Description: The money line payout odds when betting on the away team with the point spread

Name: PointSpreadHomeTeamMoneyLine
Description: The money line payout odds when betting on the home team with the point spread

Name: LastPlay
Description: The description of the most recent play/event of the game. This is for display purposes and does not include corresponding data points.

Name: IsClosed
Description: Indicates whether the game is over and the final score has been verified and closed out.

Name: Quarters
Description: The details of the quarters (including overtime periods) for this game.

Name: GameEndDateTime
Description: The date and time that the game ended in US Eastern Time

Name: HomeRotationNumber
Description: The Rotation number of the home team for this game

Name: AwayRotationNumber
Description: The Rotation number of the away team for this game

Name: QuarterID
Description: Unique identifier for each Quarter.

Name: GameID
Description: The unique ID for this game.

Name: Number
Description: The Number (Order) of the Quarter in the scope of the Game.

Name: Name
Description: The Name of the Quarter (possible values: 1; 2; 3; 4; OT; OT2; OT3; etc)

Name: AwayScore
Description: The total points scored by the away team in this Quarter.

Name: HomeScore
Description: The total points scored by the home team in this Quarter.

Name: PlayerID
Description: The player's unique PlayerID as assigned by FantasyData.

Name: SportsDataID
Description: Deprecated. Use SportRadarPlayerID instead.

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the player's status of being on an active roster. Possible values include: Active; Inactive

Name: TeamID
Description: The TeamID of the team this player is employed by.

Name: Team
Description: The key/abbreviation of the team this player is employed by.

Name: Jersey
Description: The player's jersey number.

Name: PositionCategory
Description: The player's position category. Possible values: C; F; G

Name: Position
Description: The player's primary position. Possible values: C; PF; PG; SF; SG

Name: FirstName
Description: The player's first name.

Name: LastName
Description: The player's last name.

Name: Height
Description: The player's height in inches.

Name: Weight
Description: The player's weight in pounds (lbs).

Name: BirthDate
Description: The player's date of birth.

Name: BirthCity
Description: The city in which the player was born.

Name: BirthState
Description: The state in which the player was born.

Name: BirthCountry
Description: The country in which the player was born.

Name: HighSchool
Description: The high school that the player attended.

Name: College
Description: The college that the player attended.

Name: Salary
Description: The player's salary for the current season.

Name: PhotoUrl
Description: The URL of the player's headshot photo.

Name: Experience
Description: The number of years experience the player has in the NBA.

Name: SportRadarPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the SportRadar API.

Name: RotoworldPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the Rotoworld news feed.

Name: RotoWirePlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the RotoWire news feed.

Name: FantasyAlarmPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the FantasyAlarm news feed.

Name: StatsPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the STATS data feeds.

Name: SportsDirectPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the SportsDirect data feeds.

Name: XmlTeamPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the XML Team data feeds.

Name: InjuryStatus
Description: Indicates the player's injury status. Possible values include: Probable; Questionable; Doubtful; Out

Name: InjuryBodyPart
Description: The body part that is injured (Knee; Groin; Calf; Hamstring; etc.)

Name: InjuryStartDate
Description: The day that the injury started or first discovered.

Name: InjuryNotes
Description: Brief description of the player's injury and expected availability.

Name: FanDuelPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to FanDuel.

Name: DraftKingsPlayerID

Name: YahooPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to Yahoo Daily Fantasy Sports Contests.

Name: YahooName
Description: The player's full name in Yahoo's daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: DepthChartPosition
Description: The position of the player on the depth chart.

Name: DepthChartOrder
Description: The order of the player on the depth chart.

Description: A globally unique ID for this team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: FantasyDraftName
Description: The player's full name in FantasyDraft's daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: FantasyDraftPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to Fantasy Draft.

Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to USA Today headshot data feeds.

Description: The player's transparent background headshot URL as provided by USA Today. License from USA Today is required.

Description: The type of season that this record corresponds to (1=Regular Season; 2=Preseason; 3=Postseason; 4=Offseason; 5=AllStar).

Name: Day
Description: The day that the game is scheduled to be played in UTC.

Name: DateTime
Description: The date/time that the game is scheduled to be played in UTC.

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the game's status. Possible values include: Scheduled; InProgress; Final; Suspended; Postponed; Canceled

Name: AwayTeamId
Description: The TeamId of the away team.

Name: HomeTeamId
Description: The TeamId of the home team.

Name: AwayTeamName
Description: The name of the away team.

Name: HomeTeamName
Description: The name of the home team.

Name: GlobalGameId
Description: A globally unique ID for this game. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalAwayTeamId
Description: A globally unique ID for the away team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalHomeTeamId
Description: A globally unique ID for the home team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: PregameOdds
Description: List of Pregame GameOdds from different sportsbooks

Name: LiveOdds
Description: List of Live GameOdds from different sportsbooks

Name: HomeTeamScore
Description: Score of the home team (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: AwayTeamScore
Description: Score of the away team (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: TotalScore
Description: Total scored points in the game (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: HomeRotationNumber
Description: The Rotation number of the home team for this game

Name: AwayRotationNumber
Description: The Rotation number of the away team for this game

Name: AlternateMarketPregameOdds
Description: List of Alternate Market GameOdds from different sportsbooks (such as 1st-half; 1st-qtr; etc)

Name: PlayerID
Description: The PlayerID of the player

Name: GameID
Description: The GameID of the game

Name: Name
Description: The full name of the player

Name: Opponent
Description: The TeamKey of the opponent in the game

Name: Team
Description: The TeamKey of the player's team in the game

Name: DateTime
Description: The start time of the game (to give an idea of when prop should close)

Name: Description
Description: A description of the stat the over/under is referring to (ex: Three Pointers Made)

Name: OverUnder
Description: The over under value in question (ex: 1.5)

Name: OverPayout
Description: The (american styled) payout for a successful over bet.

Name: UnderPayout
Description: The (american styled) payout for a successful under bet.

Name: BetResult
Description: A description of the result (Over; Under; or Push)

Name: StatResult
Description: The final total from the game of the stat in question

Name: PlayerID
Description: Unique ID of the Player (assigned by FantasyData).

Name: Name
Description: Name of Player.

Name: TeamID
Description: Unique ID of the Team the player belongs to (assigned by FantasyData).

Name: Team
Description: Name of the team the player belongs to.

Name: Position
Description: Position player plays.

Name: PreferredHostedHeadshotUrl
Description: The player's preferred hosted headshot URL. This returns the headshot with transparent background; if available.

Name: PreferredHostedHeadshotUpdated
Description: The last updated date of the player's preferred hosted headshot.

Name: HostedHeadshotWithBackgroundUrl
Description: The player's hosted headshot URL.

Name: HostedHeadshotWithBackgroundUpdated
Description: The last updated date of the player's hosted headshot.

Name: HostedHeadshotNoBackgroundUrl
Description: The player's transparent background hosted headshot URL.

Name: HostedHeadshotNoBackgroundUpdated
Description: The last updated date of the player's transparent background hosted headshot.
